{"tid":688483,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被打到臨陣換將？中國財政部副長說完話7分鐘後被免職","createTime":"2018-06-03T09:13:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-04T01:05:27.000Z","uid":141151,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"6ca711f978582b131142e34a0f7a5a73a2c5d42f","tid":688483,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T09:13:57.000Z","msg":"被打到臨陣換將？中國財政部副長說完話7分鐘後被免職<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/business/breakingnews/2446104\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbusiness%2Fbreakingnews%2F2446104&d=EKBlxs2ezAfNZLerYJAvG54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=8240eaab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbusiness%2Fbreakingnews%2F2446104&h=79598095\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/business/breakingnews/2446104</a><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美中貿易戰日前開打，美國祭出加徵關稅手段，中國也不甘示弱用同一招反擊，近來才逐漸趨緩，仍在持續協商貿易問題。但就在此時，一直以來參與美中溝通的中國財政部副部長朱光耀，6月1日出來澄清中國降低關稅問題，卻在7分鐘後突然遭到免職。<br />\n<br />\n中國國務院當天發布國家人員任免公告，朱光耀被撤換財政部副部長職務，由廖岷接替。同一時間還有國務院國有資產監督管理委員會副主任黃丹華、中國科學院副院長張傑、中國證券監督管理委員會副主席姜洋被免職。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，朱光耀6月1日下午才剛出來澄清，中國最近願意調降關稅是主動執行的，並非受到美國強迫，結果下午4時49分新聞才剛上稿，4時56分國務院就發布撤換公告，可以說是放話後7分鐘就遭到撤換。網民對此議論紛紛，有人認為這顯示出中國對於貿易戰有主戰主和兩派正爭執不下。<br />\n<br />\n據《美國之音》報導，朱光耀從2010年5月就職後，擔任中國財政部副部長迄今已有8年，而接任朱光耀職位的廖岷，先前是中國中央財經委員會辦公室副主任，是習近平親信劉鶴的副手。"},{"pid":"be51db161e15d47c094e17710149ef2a886ce24c","tid":688483,"uid":37808,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T09:18:38.000Z","msg":"中國成..."},{"pid":"f79127efa760153a780368c519bb8cd0225a3c4b","tid":688483,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be51db161e15d47c094e17710149ef2a886ce24c","tid":688483,"uid":37808,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T09:18:38.000Z","msg":"中國成..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T09:19:49.000Z","msg":"最大贏家"},{"pid":"8a327aff2965e59189d12a3e4a8a40269dbcfecb","tid":688483,"uid":104699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T09:34:38.000Z","msg":"贏啦～"},{"pid":"6e0244c2fb958f8e55451bcade9d68025619917a","tid":688483,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T09:46:29.000Z","msg":"過期condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f333dac91abdf3224efb597573065313bac6be47","tid":688483,"uid":176366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T09:49:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"822363adbde8a2324d60f74f86f03912e3972db0","tid":688483,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T09:50:30.000Z","msg":"喂 咁樣算係贏定唔贏先？"},{"pid":"346ffd2d05af6d03a1c90c43738c841c1fa3278a","tid":688483,"uid":157535,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T10:05:30.000Z","msg":"人治社會做咩位都無保障<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d10dbfda892e0b4bd6bc3071c29bb9a2944318c","tid":688483,"uid":76310,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T10:08:44.000Z","msg":"貿易戰都有黨爭<br />\n主戰主和<br />\n<br />\n十足十古代咁"},{"pid":"2980477eb95a597b951a2c868f3691fe5022afb8","tid":688483,"uid":98289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T13:48:04.000Z","msg":"而接任朱光耀職位的廖岷，先前是中國中央財經委員會辦公室副主任，是習近平親信劉鶴的副手<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又係靠關係<br />\n有冇料到傢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f97f711e5ec5b30cd406ca26353baa49a2b0682","tid":688483,"uid":63779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T13:50